03:04.067 --> 03:06.567
Bocce, the ancient
game of kings.

03:06.600 --> 03:10.167
Throw the little ball, try and
get the other balls close.

03:10.200 --> 03:13.133
Closer than the other guy's.

03:15.600 --> 03:18.533
Gene, Uncle Gene,
this is Anthony Bourdain.

03:18.567 --> 03:21.467
