05:06.833 --> 05:08.967
Here, Gene. Hey.

05:09.000 --> 05:11.233
Uncle Eugene can
take care of it.

05:19.333 --> 05:21.000
Oh, no way.

05:21.033 --> 05:23.633
Oh!

05:23.667 --> 05:26.567
That was the... oh, man.

05:26.600 --> 05:28.000
103 years old.

05:28.033 --> 05:30.133
