salsiccia and meatballs

06:06.833 --> 06:09.467
onto the cold, wet ground.

06:09.500 --> 06:11.533
- They're still good.
- That's still good.

06:11.567 --> 06:14.967
- Yeah.
- No.

06:15.000 --> 06:17.300
These things are gonna fly away.

