Now, wait a minute.

08:11.933 --> 08:14.300
Sixth largest in America,
now 63rd.

08:14.333 --> 08:17.467
- 63rd, yeah.
- So what happened?

08:17.500 --> 08:21.300
Well, the steel industry
began to falter in the 1960s,

08:21.333 --> 08:24.067
and by the 1980s
it was essentially dead.

08:24.100 --> 08:26.967
In the 1980s,
this place was a ghost town.

08:27.000 --> 08:28.800
We lost half of our population.

08:28.833 --> 08:30.333
It went away.
Right.

08:30.367 --> 08:32.332
And half of your population
means at least half,

08:32.366 --> 08:34.033
if not more, of your tax base.

08:34.067 --> 08:36.633
- So what went right?
- What went right?

08:36.667 --> 08:39.700
