is what went wrong.

08:39.732 --> 08:43.732
It became attractive to
people outside of Pittsburgh

08:43.767 --> 08:46.000
because it's super affordable.

08:48.433 --> 08:51.833
Bow down to your new
masters, your techie future,

08:51.867 --> 08:56.000
the robot overlords
of a shiny, new Pittsburgh.

